<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='352000' id='t-352000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='354000' id='t-354000'>But if questions affect human well-being</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='356000' id='t-356000'>then they do have answers, whether or not we can find them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='359000' id='t-359000'>And just admitting this --</span>
