<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='707000' id='t-707000'>Now, to say this is not to say that we have got the</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='709000' id='t-709000'>perfect solution in our own society.</span>
